==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: zài jiā kào fùmŭ, chū wài kào péngyŏu
===Proverb===
'''[[在]][[家]][[靠]][[父母]]，[[出]][[外]][[靠]][[朋友]]'''
# At home, you rely on your parents.  Away from home, you rely on your friends.
